Utils

  The "Utils" package provides useful objects for mathematical or geometrical handlings.

* Utils Presentation

  Implemented classes are :
  
  * <<Position/Velocity>> object, used to describe moving points by their position/velocity 
  coordinates in a given frame, and associated useful operations.

  * <<Line>> object, used to represent a geometric line and associated useful operations.

